main event: An unidentified flying object was sighted in Annapolis, Maryland, on July 6, 1956.
interesting points: The object was approximately 30 feet in diameter and oval in shape,The UFO hovered at an altitude of about 1,000 feet and emitted a bright, glowing light,The sighting occurred around 9:45 P.M. and lasted for several minutes before the object rapidly accelerated and left the area,The incident caused alarm among the observer and others who witnessed it,The report concluded that further investigation was recommended as the object remained unidentified.
sighted object: an oval-shaped UFO approximately 30 feet in diameter
witness description: A reliable and credible civilian resident of Annapolis, Maryland
